\title{Writing changelogs}

\p{[Changelogs](changelog), which appear chronologically on the homepage, are
designed to give brief summaries of recent additions in the library as well as give
some human insight about the process, such as interesting surprising mathematical
results, or insights into the experience of formalising a known result. Changelogs
are not intended to be in 1-to-1 correspondence with pull requests; however first
time contributors are encouraged to write a changelog for non-trivial pull requests.}

\p{New changelog entries can follow the template from recent entries, including
using a \code{\startverb \meta{external}{LINKTOPR} \stopverb} tag to link to the
relevant PRs.}
